Welcome to Shenanigans Sports Pub
Our Food
Our Atmosphere
Our Atmosphere
At Shenanigans Sports Pub, we specialize in traditional American food.
Our dishes are made using authentic recipes and ingredients, ensuring that every bite is full of flavor and happiness. We also offer a wide selection of wines, craft cocktails, and draft beers to complement your meal.
Our Atmosphere
Our Atmosphere
Our Atmosphere
Step into Shenanigans Sports Pub and you will be transported to our piece of paradise.. Our restaurant features a vibrant and welcoming atmosphere that is perfect for a date night, family dinner, or special occasion. Our friendly, beautiful, and uniquely crafted staff will make you feel right at home. South FL Style.
Our History
Our Atmosphere
Our History
Pat and Christine, owners of Shenanigans Sports Pub have been serving the community for over 30 years. We started as a small family owned restaurant and have grown to become a beloved local establishment. We are proud to become a staple in the community and look forward to many more years of serving our customers.
Frequently Asked Questions
Please reach us at  if you cannot find an answer to your question.
Does Shenanigans Sports Pub offer takeout?
Yes, Shenanigans Sports Pub offers takeout.
What is the price range of Shenanigans Sports Pub?
The price range at Shenanigans Sports Pub varies depending on the dish and time of day. Our menu offers options to suit a range of budgets.
Does Shenanigans have Delivery?
Yes, Check us out on Door Dash and UberEats
Does Shenanigans have a Drive- Thru?
Yes, we do!
